title: Weekly Wrap: "Game Of Chicken."
description: Sam can't believe we made it this week with Haley Byrd (@byrdinator), congressional reporter for The Weekly Standard, and Lissandra Villa (@LissandraVilla), political reporter for BuzzFeed News. They talk through the most dominant story of the week: immigration.  Email samsanders@npr.org or tweet @NPRItsBeenAMin with feels.
